106
00:04:30,352 --> 00:04:31,187
Thanks, Bill.

107
00:04:31,294 --> 00:04:35,769
I'm reporting from the Razzle Dazzle Supermarket on 75th and Columbus...

108
00:04:35,876 --> 00:04:37,571
75th and Columbus.

109
00:04:38,703 --> 00:04:40,023
