151
00:06:26,081 --> 00:06:28,354
No, I'm across the room at my drafting table,

152
00:06:28,415 --> 00:06:32,166
showing some foxy young thing all my cool architect stuff.

153
00:06:32,239 --> 00:06:33,913
So, Robin strolls over,

154
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:38,297
and I casually give her one of these: "Hey, what's up?"

155
00:06:38,373 --> 00:06:42,294
She says, "Hey, nice place, et cetera, et cetera."

156
00:06:42,377 --> 00:06:43,847
And then, I say,

157
00:06:43,908 --> 00:06:45,649
"Well, make yourself at home."

158
00:06:45,721 --> 00:06:48,445
And, I casually return to my conversation.

159
00:06:48,634 --> 00:06:50,590
