160
00:06:51,505 --> 00:06:54,791
"Oh, you're still here?" I say, 

161
00:06:54,855 --> 00:06:57,799
like I don't really care, but it's a nice surprise.

162
00:06:57,871 --> 00:06:59,620
And then, very casually:

163
00:07:00,313 --> 00:07:02,402
"Want to see the roof?"

164
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:04,855
The roof!

165
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:07,608
Get her up to the roof, and the roof takes care of the rest.

166
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:09,063
