Oh, the moon, the stars, the shimmering skyline.

168
00:07:12,882 --> 00:07:15,626
You can't not fall in love on that roof.

169
00:07:16,714 --> 00:07:18,688
We do it up there, sometimes.

170
00:07:19,017 --> 00:07:20,941
Solid plan, my little friend.

171
00:07:21,001 --> 00:07:21,934
We're the same height.

172
00:07:21,996 --> 00:07:25,267
