253
00:10:42,476 --> 00:10:44,503
Hi, you!

254
00:10:44,575 --> 00:10:45,477
You're back!

255
00:10:45,548 --> 00:10:46,751
I sure am.

256
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,985
Come on, sweetie, I need a drink.

257
00:10:51,077 --> 00:10:52,582
